{"tid":206473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CC台今日咁亂, 係時候重提蔣巴既\"解決五毛專案\"","createTime":"2017-04-18T11:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T12:39:43.000Z","uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f26756e329425009afcafbc56c2fc0b9257510f","tid":206473,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"我地趕錯蔣囝了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/161569/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/161569/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n蔣介石（翻生）1 個月前<br />\n由於連登近日遭到五毛攻擊,身為會員不能坐視不理!<br />\n故此本人提出下列建議:<br />\n<br />\n1)模仿膠登推出類似&quot;內務長&quot;性質的職位,並賦予其BAN五毛的權力.<br />\n2)該職位隸屬連尼住及其管理團隊<br />\n3)一人一票選出,如會員不滿可發動罷免公投,當公投成立,重選!<br />\n4)如會員發現五毛,請開POST公投,當公投成立即ban.<br />\n5)刑罰:1次就ban3日,3次以上就ban25日,多個10次就365日<br />\n6)如經過上述刑罰仍不悔改,會員可發動&quot;永久停帳公投&quot;當公投成立,該帳號永久停用.<br />\n7)該職位每六個月舉行選舉<br />\n8)當選兩次,便不能連任<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"3e30b10cff8c949fd73a4ea49d9e4ce2711a3fc3","tid":206473,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T11:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a867b818a7d725cb66d87c8bc7f12f9eb6d3ff93","tid":206473,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"芝麻雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b843b8a01037802f01ec4b8464c70c71e5d51273","tid":206473,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"最後實變鳩ban"},{"pid":"5f5fe96182022f04873ad6cddf124c5d6e707a40","tid":206473,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_15.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_15.gif&h=6860f8c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/180236_98